9cc2ca5bfa9fd27ddcf","user_type":"people","headline":"学渣一枚","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559819775","thumbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-fdab6e27c4a4585f65e80b865efb644d_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545785628,"updated_time":1545785628,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":1,"content":"\u003cp\u003e证明了哥德巴赫猜想。。。嗯嗯嗯大概率我认为是错误的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e        我先说明一下不是在嘲讽题主。想问一下题主学过数论没有。如果没有学过，那么证明肯定会有问题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e        如果作为高中生自学过数论，说明题主数学上平日成绩优异有空余时间钻研别的。建议好好学习，考个好大学或者去数学竞赛。没必要拿哥德巴赫猜想这种噱头混什么保送(坐等1月1日你论文发表再说)。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e         顺便说一下这学期我们正好学数论，数论的难度我是有些了解的。。。。好难啊    \u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-07258f9354d93307401c3147164b3a36_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"559\" data-rawheight=\"332\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-959c0d85a1bb41494c47a98dc10f5df0_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"559\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-07258f9354d93307401c3147164b3a36_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='559'%20height='332'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"559\" data-rawheight=\"332\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-959c0d85a1bb41494c47a98dc10f5df0_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"559\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-07258f9354d93307401c3147164b3a36_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-07258f9354d93307401c3147164b3a36_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559806909,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","creat